WebTableHeaderHasIdOrScopeCheck2"<th>" tags should have "id" or "scope" attributes"MAJOR*web:í$<p>Associating <code>&lt;table&gt;</code> headers, i.e. <code>&lt;th&gt;</code> elements, with their <code>&lt;td&gt;</code> cells enables screen
