csharpsquidS2589,Boolean expressions should not be gratuitous"MAJOR*cs:˝
<p>If a boolean expression doesn‚Äôt change the evaluation of the condition, then it is entirely unnecessary, and can be removed. If it is gratuitous
because it does not match the programmer‚Äôs intent, then it‚Äôs a bug and the expression should be fixed.</p>
