<p>In both cases, Galois/Counter Mode (GCM) with no padding should be preferred. As the .NET framework doesn‚Äôt provide this natively, the use of a
certified third party lib is recommended.</p>
<p>This rule raises an issue when any of the following CipherMode is detected: ECB, CBC, OFB, CFB, CTS.</p>
