href="https://www.owasp.org/index.php/Server_Side_Request_Forgery">SSRFs</a>.</p>
<p>Example in this XML document, an external entity read the /etc/passwd file:</p>
<pre>
&lt;?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?&gt;
